#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, vec2 C)
{
    vec3 p,r=iResolution,c=vec3(0),
    d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,.7));
    float i=0.,s,e,g=0.,t=iTime;
	for(;i++<90.;){
        p=g*d;
        p=R(p,normalize(H(t*.1)),g*.1);
        p.z+=t;
        p=abs(asin(.7*sin(p)));
        s=1.5;
        vec4 q=vec4(p,.5);
        for(int i=0;i++<7;)
            s*=e=max(1.1/dot(q,q),1.2),
            q=abs(q-.04)*e-vec4(.7,1.2,1.1,1.2);
        g+=e=length(q.xz)*length(q.wy)/s;
	    c+=mix(vec3(1),H(p.z*.8),.6)*.02/exp(.05*i*i*e);
	}
	c*=c;
    O=vec4(c,1);
}
